    "description": "Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Investment Banker at our Mysuru location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions:\nUnion Bank of India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Union Bank of India Ventures Solutions!",
